name: Blob Punks
description: Adventuring into the unknown, 5257 Brave Punks have entered the Blockchain encapsulated in Blobs. The inscription left on this transaction will serve as a memory long after their on-chain demise. They are a free, no-roadmap, good-vibes fair mint. They encapsulate punk culture as we wave them farewell into the blob abyss. They are the Blob Punks
